reviewText:
I want to say that I LIKE THE GAME but IT ABSOLUTELY NEEDS:

- a better viewing angle to see the pool table better;
- better servers because often it doesn't connect;
- a better menu graphics;
- a graphic optimization for lower pc's (I got a 2.1Mhz processor, but it goes slow also with low settings)
- more typology of game (such as italian pool")

After that I'll suggest this game to all my friends ;)"
